<TR><TD colspan=2>
<tr bgcolor="#ffffee"><td align="left" valign="top"><b>[Illiad] THE MAGICAL STEAM-POWERED NOTIFICAT-A-TRON</b></td><td align="right" valign="top">Posted:Wed Dec  1 08:27:59 2010</td></tr>
<tr bgcolor="white"><td colspan=3><img width="72" height="72" align="left" hspace=9 vspace=9 src="http://www.userfriendly.org/images/icons/administrivia.png">As promised, I have a simple, old-style solution for those who just want to be notified when a new UF 'toon is published. I give you <A HREF="http://www.friendlyuser.org/UFUpdates/mail.cgi/list/ufupdates/">a mailing list</A> which will only mail you in three instances: when a new 'toon or arc is published, mailing list admin notices, and general UF admin announcments. We expect the frequency of mailings to be pleasantly low. Subscription and unsubscription are simple and instant -- none of this "we'll take your name off our list in ten days" business.<BR clear=all><a href="http://ars.userfriendly.org/news/?id=1291220879"><img src="http://graphics.userfriendly.org/images/usercomments.gif" width="60" height="18" alt="User Comments" border="0"></a></td></tr>

</td></tr>
